Name: depayco
Version: 1.0.3
Summary: Django integration with ePayco (epayco.co)
Home-page: https://github.com/ma1onso/depayco
Author: Alonso
Author-email: alons45@gmail.com
License: GPL
Description: Django integration with ePayco ([epayco.co](https://www.epayco.co)), Colombian payment gateway.
        
        ## Installation
        - `pip install depayco`.
        
        - Set _depayco_ on INSTALLED_APPS.
        
        - Run `python manage.py migrate`.
        
        ## Configurations (settings.py)
        
        **EPAYCO_PUBLIC_KEY**: String
        
        **EPAYCO_SECRET_KEY**: String
        
        **DEBUG_EPAYCO**: Boolean
        
        **PLANS**
        ```
        PLANS = (
            {
                'id_plan': 'love2d_course',
                'name': 'love2d Course',
                'description': 'The most beautiful love2d course',
                'amount': 29.99,
                'currency': 'USD',
                'interval': 'month',
                'interval_count': 1,
                'trial_days': 14,
            },
            {
                'id_plan': 'defold_course',
                'name': 'defold Course',
                'description': 'The most mad defold course',
                'amount': 29.99,
                'currency': 'USD',
                'interval': 'month',
                'interval_count': 1,
                'trial_days': 14,
            }
        )
        ```
        
        ## How to use
        
        `python manage.py sync_plans` to create plans on epayco.co
        
